Title: User is able to create a booking without phone number

Description: If user sends a POST request to create a booking without phone number. API returns 200 status code

Steps to reproduce:
    1. Send a POST request to create a booking without phone number in it's body
    2. Verify response

Expected: 400 status code and some meaningful error message like "must not be null"

Actual: 200 status code and empty response body

Note: Might not be an issue, but should be clarified

Screen recording: https://imgur.com/a/pa2NgSv

Example json payload:
{
    "bookingid": 138,
    "roomid": 222,
    "firstname": "Tripp",
    "lastname": "Phelipeau",
    "depositpaid": true,
    "email": "tphelipeau0@constantcontact.com",
    "bookingdates": {
        "checkin": "2025-08-28",
        "checkout": "2025-09-04"
    }
}